data.description: Welcome home to this stunning 3 bed, 2.5 bath bi-level gem in the heart of Hebron, IN! The open concept design seamlessly blends the spacious living room, dining area, and modern kitchen, creating a perfect hub for entertaining or gatherings. The primary bedroom boasts a luxurious ensuite, providing a comfortable retreat within your new home. Impeccably maintained and move-in ready, this residence offers both comfort and style. Step outside to discover an inviting open backyard, ideal for outdoor activities and relaxation. With its prime location and thoughtful design, this property epitomizes the best in contemporary living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this Hebron beauty your own!
